      <title>希腊在未来12年内花费250亿欧元的国防</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/greece-to-spend-25-billion-on-defense-over-the-next-12-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理凯里亚科斯·西塔基斯（Kyriakos Mitsakis）周三表示，希腊将在2037年在国防上花费250亿欧元（270亿美元），周三表示，他揭露了政府为提高军事能力的12年战略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/greece-to-spend-25-billion-on-defense-over-the-next-12-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 08:42:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国人在勒笔获得生命线时承受压力的最大右</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/french-far-right-to-keep-up-pressure-as-le-pen-gets-lifeline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国的国家集会计划抗议它所谓的“法官暴政”，即使上诉法院在周二晚些时候在一份惊喜声明中表示，它应该能够在2026年中期对Marine Le Pen的挑战进行裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/french-far-right-to-keep-up-pressure-as-le-pen-gets-lifeline</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 08:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非预算投票测试联盟，投资者信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/south-african-budget-vote-set-to</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非议会将对联合政府之间的谈判地位的不确定性进行不确定性，以解决他们在支出计划上的差异，这将在一项关键的预算立法上进行投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/south-african-budget-vote-set-to</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 07:06:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚雇用壳牌部门的前首席执行官领导国家石油公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/nigeria-hires-ex-ceo-of-shell-unit-to-lead-state-oil-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布（Bola Tinubu）聘请了壳牌公司的前负责人来经营国家石油公司，因为非洲最大的原油生产商致力于提高产出和为首次公开募股做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/nigeria-hires-ex-ceo-of-shell-unit-to-lead-state-oil-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 05:33:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列扩大针对加沙哈马斯的地面行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/israel-expands-ground-operations-in-gaza-in-push-against-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列命令巴勒斯坦领土南部的人们离开加沙的军事行动，以准备与哈马斯进行更激烈的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/israel-expands-ground-operations-in-gaza-in-push-against-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 04:31:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸军方向中国救济车队开枪的“警告”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/myanmar-junta-rejects-ceasefire-proposals-as-quake-deaths-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸军方表示，它向中国红十字会的车队发射了“警告镜头”，这在周五的地震中摧毁了该国的中部地区，该地震炸死了2800多人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/myanmar-junta-rejects-ceasefire-proposals-as-quake-deaths-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 02:38:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由民主党支持的法官在威斯康星州竞选中击败了马斯克的候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/musk-backed-candidate-defeated-in-wisconsin-supreme-court-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的候选人在威斯康星州的司法竞赛中遭受了巨大的损失，尽管世界上最富有的人向竞选活动投入了数百万美元，而共和党人则避免在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）家乡佛罗里达州的两个关键的美国众议院席位中感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/musk-backed-candidate-defeated-in-wisconsin-supreme-court-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 02:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国模拟台湾演习第二天的港口罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-holds-second-day-of-exercises-near-taiwan-squeezing-lai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国周三在台湾周围进行了第二天的演习，这加剧了它对赖斯总统的前所未有的军事压力，它非常不喜欢它。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-holds-second-day-of-exercises-near-taiwan-squeezing-lai</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 00:44:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>两党参议员小组重新对俄罗斯的新制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/bipartisan-group-of-senators-readies-new-sanctions-to-hit-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）拒绝与乌克兰进行善意的停火谈判或违反最终协议，则有50名共和党和民主党参议员提出了制裁计划，以打击俄罗斯和购买石油的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/bipartisan-group-of-senators-readies-new-sanctions-to-hit-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 22:18:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
